# Cloudflare Pages Redirects
# https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/

# Enforce clean URLs without trailing slashes
# The ! forces the redirect even when the page exists

# Articles
/articles/:slug/  /articles/:slug  301!

# Article tags
/articles/tags/:tag/  /articles/tags/:tag  301!
/articles/tags/  /articles/tags  301!

# Articles index
/articles/  /articles  301!

# Subscribe success
/subscribe-success/  /subscribe-success  301!

# Legacy privacy policy (removed during Remix migration)
/privacy-policy  /  301
